{"tid":1949920,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"首粵語歌紅出台灣","createTime":"2020-03-30T03:53:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-31T07:44:00.000Z","uid":343574,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fb16502ab5afc7353d624f0c49572826de9d4a84","tid":1949920,"uid":343574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T03:53:20.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/aZHLn1Xyo7c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaZHLn1Xyo7c&d=UCtUugLpQcFJMmY1nWpYqz4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=db694e02\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aZHLn1Xyo7c</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/87F2MD2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F87F2MD2.png&h=4a2c67e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n首歌係好聽，但其實發生乜撚野事，最撚諷刺係香港地咁撚多唱得歌嘅人，竟然一個台灣人搶左去唱粵語歌<br />\n<br />\n第一次聽，之後唸住查下個歌手咩料唸住follow下，屌台灣人黎嘅<br />\n<br />\n係好聽嘅，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">不過真係好撚諷刺lor屌</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再查多下，原來係tvb星夢，唔撚怪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fc09fd5331b922c8aa6d939740a01af56922198","tid":1949920,"uid":221571,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T03:55:55.000Z","msg":"姐係咁講<br />\n香港人係咪唔出得國語歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黃明志係咪都唔應該唱粵語歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"121d3b0968121a5819210c4bba6382ac6b2103df","tid":1949920,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T04:02:02.000Z","msg":"咩呀 記得佢係後生仔傾下計<br />\n佢台灣人黎<br />\n咁台灣人撐返佢都好正常姐"},{"pid":"040012a2fbd5718fc25a12b8689f7a0ee7337fdf","tid":1949920,"uid":343574,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"3fc09fd5331b922c8aa6d939740a01af56922198","tid":1949920,"uid":221571,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T03:55:55.000Z","msg":"姐係咁講<br />\n香港人係咪唔出得國語歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黃明志係咪都唔應該唱粵語歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T04:11:58.000Z","msg":"你係咪閱讀能力有問題，我背後思想講緊係成個香港音樂點解咁撚慘<br />\n<br />\n你覺得一個台灣人第一首派台歌 出道歌係粵語無問題？<br />\n真係咁講，呢條台灣佬算得係乜皮，我敢講佢都係垃圾港豬or紅藍人黎，至少唔會係黃，<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">佢嘅存在係剝削緊我地香港本土嘅文化，你覺得咁樣係無問題？我真係恭喜你啊</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n我地香港有咁多唱得歌嘅人，點解係佢搶左個位黎做，當然我唔係想批評呢位歌手，香港娛樂公司先係幕後黑手<br />\n<br />\n另外你話香港人係咪唔「出」得國語歌，可以呀，好似啊鄧紫棋咁，懷抱祖國人民幣幾開心。<br />\n<br />\n另外你話黃明志，不如音樂造詣高小小先再出黎柒，人地黃明志一直以黎都咁愛國，又第一首歌 去到派台人地都係堅持緊人地本土文化，之後因為紅左要吸納粉絲圈子先開始出現唔同文化嘅音樂，但佢個人tokkok依然有去宣傳本地文化<br />\n<br />\n你認識唔夠深就唔好走出黎柒<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hfN4Z6L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhfN4Z6L.png&h=f57f0c51&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bb9ec7fd761fb614ec4c6d39227d595c6f40d845","tid":1949920,"uid":343574,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"121d3b0968121a5819210c4bba6382ac6b2103df","tid":1949920,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T04:02:02.000Z","msg":"咩呀 記得佢係後生仔傾下計<br />\n佢台灣人黎<br />\n咁台灣人撐返佢都好正常姐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T04:14:32.000Z","msg":"最撚諷刺係咩，香港有咁撚多人唱得歌，跳得舞，演得戲，然而之後呢？<br />\n<br />\n咪發夢喇香港人，翻工喇"},{"pid":"16a4f2cd54d5726570d4f10879fc858a01ee8818","tid":1949920,"uid":343574,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3fc09fd5331b922c8aa6d939740a01af56922198","tid":1949920,"uid":221571,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T03:55:55.000Z","msg":"姐係咁講<br />\n香港人係咪唔出得國語歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n黃明志係咪都唔應該唱粵語歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-30T04:16:31.000Z","msg":"懶係醒咁<br />\n<br />\n好明顯你就唔撚知香港音樂人到底有幾咁慘"},{"pid":"3eb0185ff09cd225ca1ae2aff51953b6f73dc90d","tid":1949920,"u