own.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你可以用音樂去展示一個地區或國家嘅語言特色甚至本土文化<br />\n但唔係叫你攞嚟做長城圍住自己<br />\n你應該問嘅係點解香港人唔多啲撐香港本土歌手同音樂<br />\n而家走去屌外來人唱粵語唱飯碗<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78758cf2ac91bf02ef986b8eae3c91ca5eedb690","tid":1949920,"uid":148756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:15:40.000Z","msg":"成首歌驟耳聽似係福音團體整pop song,成件事有點低成本製作feel,首歌未到&ldquo;好聽&rdquo;呢個level喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db14a4d66c61dd9be0a36c5605effb99689ed085","tid":1949920,"uid":343574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"78758cf2ac91bf02ef986b8eae3c91ca5eedb690","tid":1949920,"uid":148756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:15:40.000Z","msg":"成首歌驟耳聽似係福音團體整pop song,成件事有點低成本製作feel,首歌未到&ldquo;好聽&rdquo;呢個level喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-31T06:29:42.000Z","msg":"好唔好聽 chord progressive啲嘢我都唔太識<br />\n<br />\n但成本太低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有mv 場地費 演員費 化妝師 剪接 道具費 拍攝組 燈光組 總設計師<br />\n<br />\n音樂聽上去已經至少有四件樂器：人聲 鋼琴 吉他 鼓 弦樂（似電子），再加上場地費 器材 調音混音師<br />\n<br />\n加上其他立立雜雜utility 水電飯盒費用<br />\n<br />\n咁多野加起上黎你同我講話叫做低成本？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7a2e196b45bfc4dedd6439ab829ac29bab8ef87"